{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778977056513,"sessionID":"ses_1ccb4b5eaffeUb7ozv27eQPznG","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_y5dvObtDV92wogJ3O3xbJd3Q","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"addedBy|HRA|subsetdef:","path":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/src/ontology","include":"uberon-edit.obo"},"output":"Found 28 matches\n/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo:\n  Line 2: subsetdef: added_for_HCA \"Classes tagged with this subset property were added upon request from the Human Cell Atlas (HCA).\"\n\n  Line 3: subsetdef: common_anatomy \"Terms applicable across life, not restricted to Metazoa\"\n\n  Line 4: subsetdef: cumbo \"CUMBO\"\n\n  Line 5: subsetdef: cyclostome_subset \"cyclostome structures\"\n\n  Line 6: subsetdef: defined_by_cytoarchitecture \"brain region defined by cyto-architecture\"\n\n  Line 7: subsetdef: defined_by_ordinal_series \"classes that are defined by relative position counting from first in a series of elements along an axis in an individual organism rather than by strict homology\"\n\n  Line 8: subsetdef: developmental_classification \"developmental_classification\"\n\n  Line 9: subsetdef: dubious_grouping \"Indicates that subclasses in AOs may be inappropriately linked\"\n\n  Line 10: subsetdef: early_development \"A class that represents an early developmental structure, like a blastocyst. This part of the ontology is undergoing review to remove inappropriate grouping classes.\"\n\n  Line 11: subsetdef: efo_slim \"EFO slim\"\n\n  Line 12: subsetdef: emapa_ehdaa2 \"derived from the union of EHDAA2 and EMAPA - still to be checked\"\n\n  Line 13: subsetdef: feed_aligned \"subset of classes that have logical defs text defs and synonyms aligned with FEED\"\n\n  Line 14: subsetdef: functional_classification \"functional_classification\"\n\n  Line 15: subsetdef: grouping_class \"Subset consisting of classes creating for grouping purposes\"\n\n  Line 16: subsetdef: