{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778977153159,"sessionID":"ses_1ccb4b5eaffeUb7ozv27eQPznG","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_8tvyv1WdCjfSU4TNYcXRnfoD","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Added the `addedByHRA` subset definition to support tracking terms added by HRA and HuBMAP team members. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+Added a new ontology subset definition, `addedByHRA`, to the Uberon OBO header. This enables terms contributed or requested by HRA and HuBMAP team members to be tagged consistently.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+Issue #3672 requested a subset tag named `addedByHRA` for tracking HRA/HuBMAP-added terms. The new subset definition is placed alongside the existing `subsetdef` declarations near `added_for_HCA` and `human_reference_atlas`-related metadata.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- Confirmed no existing `addedByHRA` subset definition was present.\n+- Ran `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o /tmp/opencode/uberon-edit-validation.obo` successfully.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- [x] Read imported issue context.\n+- [x] Reviewed repository guidance and Code of Conduct.\n+- [x] Added the requested `addedByHRA` subset definition.\n+- [x] Validated OBO syntax with ROBOT.\n+- [x] Committed only the ontology file change locally.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++